videos.title: Can Jeskai Scissors Cut Through Pioneer?
videos.description:
Its time to play with Scissors (in a safe way, of course)! Ensoul Artifact and a ton of the new Aetherdrift artifacts could be a nice mix for Mendicant and Affinity enjoyers.

Today's video is brought to you by Card Kingdom. You can pick up some Magic: the Gathering cards (and help support the show) at https://www.cardkingdom.com/mtggoldfish
